                <h3>Summer Camp</h3>
                <p>Our summer language camp has been offered at the School since 2005. It is the only such program in the State. In the
                past fifteen (15) summers, more than 1200 K-12 graders from Maine, California, Connecticut, Florida, Hawaii, Idaho,
